overview.en: Qin chain，with APP，WeChat subscription and mini program，through the behavior of practicing instrument to encourage music trainers，sharing experience after practicing can influence more people to join this circle and build up an enormous account community.  Some professional media such as instrument industry website and instrument industry headline are involved in it. Eight city instrument exhibitions will build the bridge with each colleges and universities for the sake of making projects launched with millions of target persons and communicative circle.
overview.zh: 琴链，拥有APP、公众号、小程序，通过对所有音乐练习者练琴行为进行行为激励，每次练琴后分享成果达到传播分享，影响更多人加入乐器圈子，形成一个庞大的用户社群。旗下拥有，乐器产业网、乐器产业头条，等专业媒体。中国八大城市乐器展，“西安、南京、太原、济南、青岛、沈阳、石家庄、郑州”。与各大院校、大师、明星、协会建立深度合作，让项目落地起就拥有“百万垂直目标人群和千万人群传播圈”。
